Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. snippet.title: Disclosure Day | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
A film by Steven Spielberg. Disclosure Day is in theaters 06.12.26.

If you found out we weren’t alone, if someone showed you, proved it to you, would that frighten you? This summer, the truth belongs to seven billion people. 
We are coming close to … Disclosure Day. 

Universal Pictures is proud to release a new original event film created and directed by Steven Spielberg. The film stars SAG winner and Oscar® nominee Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place), Emmy and Golden Globe winner Josh O’Connor (Challengers, The Crown), Oscar® winner Colin Firth (The King’s Speech, Kingsman franchise), Eve Hewson (Bad Sisters, The Perfect Couple) and two-time Oscar® nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Based on a story by Spielberg, the screenplay is by David Koepp, whose previous work with Spielberg includes the scripts for Jurassic Park, The Lost World: Jurassic Park, War of the Worlds and Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull. Combined, those films earned more than $3 billion worldwide. Koepp also wrote the script for this 2025’s Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Disclosure Day is produced by five-time Academy Award® nominee Kristie Macosko Krieger (The Fabelmans, West Side Story) and by Spielberg for Amblin Entertainment. The executive producers are Adam Somner and Chris Brigham. 

Steven Spielberg is one of the industry’s most successful and influential filmmakers. The top-grossing director of all time, Spielberg has helmed such blockbusters as Jaws, E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial, the Indiana Jones franchise and Jurassic Park. 
 
Among his myriad honors, he is a three-time Academy Award® winner, including Oscars® for Best Director and Best Picture for Schindler’s List, which received a total of seven Oscars®, and for Best Director for Saving Private Ryan. His most recent film, The Fabelmans, was released by Universal in 2022 and received seven Academy Award® nominations, including for Directing, Best Original Screenplay, Best Actress and Best Picture.

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story centers on the long-unresolved consequences of Steve Rogers’ final choice in Endgame, revealing that his decision to remain in the past fractured reality in ways the Avengers never anticipated. As timelines splinter and the stability of the main MCU begins to erode, Steve is forced back into the conflict, confronting the personal cost of his legacy and the ripple effects of his sacrifice. The narrative hints at a corrupted alternate reality where familiar heroes took darker paths, drawing Doctor Doom into the heart of the multiversal crisis and threatening total collapse across worlds. With time itself no longer trustworthy, Rogers emerges as both the cause and the possible solution, facing a reckoning that could determine whether the prime timeline survives or is rewritten forever.

I don't wanna have to go where you don't follow

[Chorus]

I don't wanna hurt anymore
Stay in my arms if you dare
Or must I imagine you there
Don't walk away from me
I have nothing, nothing, nothing
Don't make me close one more door

Stay in my arms if you dare
Or must I imagine you there
Don't walk away from me, no
Don't walk away from me
Don't you dare walk away from me
I have nothing, nothing, nothing
If I don't have you

[Outro]
You
If I don't have you
Oh, you

snippet.title: Konstanty Drążek - Czarne Porsche bukiet róż (Oficjalny teledysk)
snippet.description:
🎬 Konstanty Drążek – Czarne Porsche bukiet róż. Nowoczesne klubowe disco polo z romantycznym klimatem –  muzyka na playlisty, muzyka do auta i piosenka z TikToka. | Od autora „Fajna Mami”, „Kaczka Dziwaczka”, „To co dziś nie wyszło” i „Las Vegas” – półfinalisty Disco Star 2024 💫

📲 Obserwuj mnie na Instagramie:
https://www.instagram.com/konstantydrazek

🎧 Słuchaj „Czarne Porsche, bukiet róż” na wszystkich platformach streamingowych: https://digitalmusic.lnk.to/konstantydrazekczarneporschebukietroz

🆕 Konstanty Drążek prezentuje nowy singiel „Czarne Porsche, bukiet róż” – lekki, chwytliwy numer z pogranicza polskiej muzyki klubowej i nowoczesnego disco polo. To historia chłopaka z dystansem do siebie, który robi wszystko, żeby zaimponować wybrance serca. Bo nie zawsze liczą się drogie symbole – czasem wystarczy vibe, odwaga i chemia „między nami”. 🌹🚗

🎥 Teledysk do „Czarne Porsche, bukiet róż” to filmowa, lekko humorystyczna opowieść o miłości, improwizacji i robieniu rzeczy po swojemu. Kontrast między tekstem a obrazem, autoironia i szybkie zwroty akcji pokazują, że nie wszystko musi być idealne – ważne, że jest prawdziwe. Klip balansuje między beką a romantycznym klimatem, zostawiając widzowi miejsce na własną interpretację.

💥 To piosenka idealna do auta, na klubowe playlisty i TikToka. Świetnie sprawdzi się w krótkich wideo, trendach, duetach i nocnym vibe’ie.


👉 Nagraj swój film z użyciem dźwięku „Czarne Porsche, bukiet róż”, oznacz mnie i udostępnij!
🔁 Subskrybuj kanał – kolejne premiery już w drodze 🚀

snippet.title: Wham! - Last Christmas (Japanese Lyrics)
snippet.description:
ワム！ - ラスト・クリスマス | Wham! - Last Christmas
Stream and download: https://wham.lnk.to/40LastChristmas
More here: https://Wham.lnk.to/Playlists
Subscribe to the Wham! YouTube Channel: https://Wham.lnk.to/YT_Subscribe  
🎧ストリーミング再生： https://WhamJP.lnk.to/LastChristmas　

【楽曲情報】
イギリスのポップ・デュオ＝ワム！（Wham!）が1984年12月にリリースしたクリスマス・ソングの金字塔「ラスト・クリスマス」。
「去年のクリスマス　君に僕の心を捧げたのに / すぐ翌日に君はそれを放り出してしまった　/　今年はもう涙はごめんだから / 誰か他の特別な人にあげることにするよ」
恋人に裏切られたクリスマスの悲しみを綴った切ない歌詞と、軽快でポップなサウンドが相まって、世界中で＜クリスマスの大定番曲＞として今なお色褪せない輝きを放ちつづける名曲です。

------------------------------------------------------
去年のクリスマス　君に僕の心を捧げたのに
すぐ翌日に君はそれを放り出してしまった
今年はもう涙はごめんだから
誰か他の特別な人にあげることにするよ

一度の失敗にすっかり尻ごみして
ずっと距離をおいているのに　君はいまだに僕の目をとらえて離さない
教えておくれ、ベイビー　僕のこと覚えてる？
そうさ、あれから1年　忘れてたって別に驚きもしないよ
（ハッピー・クリスマス）
リボンをかけて送り届けた
「愛してる」ってメッセージをつけて　あれは本気だったんだ
今になって自分がどんなに馬鹿だったかわかったよ
でも、もし今、君がキスしてくれたら　きっとまた僕は騙されてしまうんだろうな

混雑した部屋　疲れた目をした友人たち
僕は隠れてるんだ　君と、その氷のような心から
何てことだろう　君を信頼できる人だと思ってたなんて
僕？　僕はただ単に都合のいい相談相手だったんだね
心に炎を燃やした恋人の顔
ひっそり君を想っていた　なのに君は僕を引き裂いた
だけど今、僕は本当の愛を見つけた　もう二度と君に惑わされはしない
------------------------------------------------------

#Wham #ワム #LastChristmas #ラストクリスマス #クリスマス #クリスマスソング
#日本語歌詞 #和訳歌詞
